# Physics is a capability, not a layout mode. The same Spiral arrangement is
# shown twice: paused (its analytic placement held exactly) and then played
# (the sim relaxes from that placement while the Spiral stays selected).
# Force-directed is simply *no* arrangement with physics running — the fourth
# cell, a frozen free graph, is reachable too. Offline sample ring; fresh
# profile.
settle 30
key escape

open mere://alpha
settle 10
open mere://gamma
settle 30

act Layout: Spiral
settle 20
act Fit view
settle 20
capture 01_spiral_paused

# Play: the arrangement stays selected; the sim takes over from its seed.
act Play/pause physics
settle 90
capture 02_spiral_played

# Back to no arrangement (physics resumes), then freeze it — the cell that
# was unreachable while physics was welded to the layout mode.
act Layout: Force-directed
settle 60
act Play/pause physics
settle 20
capture 03_free_graph_frozen

log physics capability matrix complete
